    <div align="left" id="post_message_283129">Not sure why you say it is bad fiction...I enjoyed it, and it made me think...<br />
 <br />
That bit about people getting a face they deserve.  It seems pretty true, really...  Athletes often talk about muscle memory...I wonder if it is like that.  The face remembers the most common configuration of muscles that it uses...<br />
 <br />
I dunno.  Anyways.<br />
