    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_283258">Well, I called it Bad Fiction because if you look at the plotline, that's what it is. I wanted to write a different version of the classic plotline from terrible fiction stories. Man's family gets killed by the mob. Gunfights, explosions, etc... it's very Schwarzenegger - I wanted to take that scenario and make it readable. :<br />
<br />
And so far as faces go, I always thought it to be something along the same lines as posture. You slouch a lot, you'll naturally slouch. You grimace a lot, you'll end up turning purple and being obsessed with Chicken Nuggets.</div>
